'''Mohamed Hany Gamal El-Demerdash''' ({{langx|ar|محمد هاني جمال الدمرداش}}; born 2 February 1996) is an Egyptian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[Al Ahly SC|Al Ahly]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].<ref>{{cite news |url=https://us.soccerway.com/players/mohamed-hany-eldemerdash/396721/ |title=Mohamed Hany - Player profile |work=Soccerway |accessdate=21 March 2019}}</ref>

==International career==

On 2 December 2025, Hany was called up to the Egypt squad for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cafonline.com/afcon2025/news/egypt-name-final-28-man-squad-for-totalenergies-caf-afcon-2025-salah-leads-pharaohs-charge/|title=Egypt name final 28-man squad for TotalEnergies CAF AFCON 2025, Salah leads Pharaohs' charge|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|date=2 December 2025|access-date=12 December 2025}}</ref>

